_sText:
Hi 

Welcome to Surf_Electron

This is a surf combat map with a twist. Located in the middle of the arena, is a flag. The first team to hold the flag for a total of 2 mins, wins. A large scoreboard can be easily seen to keep track of the progress of your team.

Weapons, buy zones and health restore points are located throughout the map to aid your cause.

Thanks to Spliff and the boys on his server for hosting and making the map even better with your suggestions and support.
Come join us at 60.234.73.177:27015

Have Fun.

Credits:

Zalos for the flag prefab
